FT  16 DEC 92 / UK Company News: Deficit at Hobson reduced to Pounds 8,000
Losses at Hobson were cut from Pounds 42,000 to Pounds 8,000 pre-tax in six
months ended September 30. Turnover of Pounds 3.08m compared with Pounds
2.81m.
Both the toiletries manufacturing operation and commodities trading
activities were profitable at the operating level, although the former
suffered from low sales volumes.
Losses per share of the USM-quoted company emerged at 0.02p (0.08p).
